            "open_state_row_icon": "#6d388b",
            "open_state_collapse_icon": "#121212",
            "open_state_collapse_icon_solid": "#ffffff",
            "open_state_collapse_bg": "#6d388b",
            "open_state_content_bg": "#fefaff",
            "open_state_content_text": "#121212",
            "content": "<p>Many kids need more movement, not more screen time. The Wooden Single Leg Balance Board turns balance practice into a simple game they will want to come back to again and again.</p><p>It encourages coordination, body awareness, focus, and confidence as children step up, steady themselves, and challenge their balance one foot at a time.</p><p>Use it during playtime, obstacle courses, movement breaks, or classroom activities for a fun way to keep kids active indoors.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_p6J4hX": {
          "type": "collapsible-row",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
