            "closed_state_content_bg": "#f9f9f9",
            "closed_state_content_text": "#121212",
            "open_colors_on_hover": true,
            "open_state_border": "#d5aeea",
            "open_state_header_bg": "#fefaff",
            "open_state_header_text": "#000000",
            "open_state_row_icon": "#6d388b",
            "open_state_collapse_icon": "#121212",
            "open_state_collapse_icon_solid": "#ffffff",
            "open_state_collapse_bg": "#6d388b",
            "open_state_content_bg": "#fefaff",
            "open_state_content_text": "#121212",
            "content": "<p>The Wooden Single Leg Balance Board helps children practice important movement skills:</p><ul><li><strong>Balance & Stability</strong> - learning to steady the body while standing on one foot</li><li><strong>Coordination & Body Awareness</strong> - helping kids understand movement, posture, and control</li><li><strong>Core & Leg Strength</strong> - active play naturally engages stabilizing muscles</li><li><strong>Focus & Patience</strong> - staying balanced encourages concentration and persistence</li><li><strong>Confidence</strong> - small wins during play help kids feel proud of what their bodies can do</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
