    "collapsible_content_nJrYmE": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_content_6w9ntk": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What is the balance board used for?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>It is designed to help kids practice balance, coordination, and body awareness through play. Families often use it for balance challenges, obstacle courses, movement breaks, and active indoor play.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_njkpDd": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is it good for beginners?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. Kids can start with short, supervised turns and build confidence at their own pace. Simple games like counting seconds on one foot make it easy and fun for beginners.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_CVU4Bm": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What skills does it help support?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>It supports balance, coordination, focus, body awareness, and confidence. Because kids are stabilizing themselves while they play, it also encourages core and leg engagement in a natural way.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_ETX7yr": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Where can kids use it?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>It works best on a flat, stable surface in a playroom, classroom, or activity corner. It can also be used outdoors on smooth, dry ground with adult supervision.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_HTVjPX": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is adult supervision recommended?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, especially for younger children or first-time users. We recommend using the board on a clear surface and staying nearby while kids are learning how to balance confidently.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_Ahw39W": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What is it made of?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>It features a simple wooden construction designed for everyday active play. Wipe it clean as needed and store it in a dry place when not in use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_z4rFdy": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What if I'm not satisfied?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 90-day money-back guarantee. If it is not the right fit for your child or play space, just reach out and we will help make it right.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
